desc: Special drops from Wiz’s personal collection of clothing, one of a kind memorabilia and priceless Taylor Gang items!

layout.text:
WELCOME TO THE OFFICIAL
WIZ KHALIFA VAULT!

"The Wiz Vault is compiled of a lot of material that I used to wear, have worn, haven't worn, could've worn, should've worn. It goes to my fans, collectors or people who want to be part of something.” Wiz Khalifa

Here you will find the largest collection of Wiz Khalifa’s personal clothing, Taylor Gang exclusives, Wiz’s sneaker collection, one of a kind memorabilia items and MORE!
